headline: LKQ Q1 Earnings Call: Revenue Misses Expectations Amid Tariff and Market Headwinds
summary: Automotive parts company LKQ (NASDAQ:LKQ) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2025, with sales falling 6.5% year on year to $3.46 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.79 per share was in line with analysts’ consensus estimates.
